  "text": "There is an underlying problem, when we face the problem of vaccinations addressed to DUs. One of the underlying problems of addressing vaccination issues for DUs is the lack of specific studies focusing on this group. Vaccination schedules are extrapolated from the general population and then applied to DUs. In the 30 years since the introduction of HBV vaccination, only a single cohort study has evaluated the clinical (not only immunological) effectiveness of the HBV vaccination among DUs, a much more relevant finding than any immunological evaluation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
